ELBOWS ON PIPING FROM GAS-GAS EXCHANGER TUBESIDE OUTLET\nTO EO REACTOR INLET SHOULD BE OF MIN. 3D RADIUS; MAXIMUM\nNO. OF ELBOWS ALLOWED IS 3.
